high_descs: Face the counter in front of you.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the counter to your right.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Step back and open the cabinet under the counter in front of you.
Place the knife inside of the cabinet in front of you and close it.
Turn right then face the counter on your left.
Take a tomato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the sink to your right.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink then take it out.
Turn around and face the microwave in front of you.
Place the tomato slice by the microwave in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tomato slice next to the microwave.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the green recycling bin.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle to the left of the plate.
Move slightly left to the area of the counter to the left of the silver tea kettle.
Slice the tomato to the right of the potted plant using the knife.
Turn around, move towards the green door, then turn around and face the counter area to the right of the sink.
Open the cabinet door to the right of the sink beneath the counter, place the knife in front of the salt shaker, then close the cabinet door.
Move to the counter area to the right of the tea kettle.
Pick up a tomato slice from the sliced tomato to the right of the potted plant.
Turn left and move to the sink in front of the window.
Place the tomato slice in the sink to the left of the lettuce, wash it with water using the faucet, then allow the sink to drain, and then pick up the tomato slice from the sink.
Turn right, move towards the green recycling bin, then turn right and move to the black microwave to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the tomato slice to the right of the spoon near the edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed tomato slice on the table.
